  "title": "Video by sgadventurousduo",
  "description": "Must try food spots in Singapore!!\n\n📍One Fattened Calf Burgers\nMultiple locations\n\n📍Shang Hai La Mian Xiao Long Bao\nMultiple locations\n\n📍Meadesmoore Steakhouse\n21A Boon Tat Street Level 2 Located near, Telok Ayer St, 069620\n\nOpening hours as per Google:\nMon-Wed: 11:30 am–3 pm, 5:30–10 pm\nThurs and Fri: 11:30 am–3 pm, 5:30–11 pm\nSat: 5.30-11pm\nSun: closed\n\n📍FYP (For You People) Cafe - Orchard Central\n181 Orchard Rd, #04-22 Orchard Central Singapore 238896\n\nOpening hours as per Google: \nMon-Thurs: 12–9:30 pm\nFri: 12–10.30pm\nSat: 11 am–10:30 pm\nSun: 11 am–9:30 pm\n\n📍千両 sen-ryo (ION Orchard)\n2 Orchard Turn, #03 - 17/18, Singapore 238801\n\nOpening hours as per Google: \nDaily: 11 am–10 pm\n\n📍Hot Duck\n1 North Point Dr, B2-147, Southwing 768019\n\nOpening hours as per Google:\nDaily: 11:30 am–10 pm\n\n📍Khao Hom\nMultiple locations\n\n📍Sin Heng Kee Porridge \nMultiple locations\n\n📍Common Man Coffee Roasters\nMultiple locations\n\n📍Nassim Hill Bakery Bistro Bar\n56 Tanglin Rd, #01-03, Singapore 247964\n\nOpening hours as per Google:\nTue-Sun: 8 am–10 pm\nMon: closed\n\n📍Fiie’s Cafe\nMultiple locations \n\n📍A Hot Hideout\nMultiple locations",
